quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  8,45,"Yaa warra amantan! Yeroo garee (diinaa) wahii qunnamtan, gadi dhaabbadhaa; akka milkooftaniifis (faaruu) baay’ee Rabbiin faarsaa"
  8,46,"Rabbiifi ergamaa Isaatiifis ajajamaa; walis hin morminaa; luynoomtanii humni keessanis (isin irraa) ni deemtii; obsaaDhugumatti, Rabbiin obsitoota wajjin jira"
  8,47,"Akka isaan boonaa, namootatti of argisiisiisan ta’anii, karaa Rabbii irraas (namoota) dhorgaa, manneen isaanii irraa bahanii hin ta’inaaRabbiin waan isaan dalaganitti marsaadha"
  8,48,"Yeroo sheyxaanni dalagaa isaanii (gadhee) miidhagsee, “har’a nama irraa injifataan isiniif hin jiruAnis gargaaraa keessan” jedheen san [yaadadhu]Yeroma gareen lamaan wal argan, of duuba deebi’ee “Dhugumatti, ani isin irraa qulqulluudha; ani waan isin hin agarren argaa jiraAni Rabbiinin sodaadhaRabbiin adabbiin Isaa cimaadha” jedhe"